name: Amnesia
description:
Mixing

This model is a continuation of my old Buttonmix, mixed using the scientific process of "Inebriated Mixing". I don't remember what exactly was put in, or at what weights, just that it looks pretty and after a little finer touch ups it's very accepting of LoRas.

Tips on Use

This model does not need quality prompts from what I've tested, and does well with booru tag prompting. The base style is semi-realistic therefore;

To increase anime aesthetic use [anime line art style:0.X]

To increase realism use (realistic:X.X)

Use lots of LoRas.
